reviewText: It was basically just 5 or 6 shows. Some I have never seen. There were a lot of episodes though and it kept the baby entertained.
Arrived in a timely manner & my daughter loves it.
great DVD for the DVD player in the car
3 stars because my son did not like this video.  It catches his attention for about 3 minutes and then he has no interest. My son is autistic though so it's not a bad video,  just didn't work for us.
